hidden mate themes like this, are once in a lifetime... by sacrificing the Queen, black makes way for Nf3 with checkmate... the only way to escape mate, is Qd3, Nf3+, Qxf3, Qxf3, and losing his own Queen... after Nxd4, Qxg1+, Ke2, Qf1+, Ke3 (Kf3, Bg2+, Ke3 or mate), exd4+... 

so white resigned...
